Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.48,0:01:45.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs60}策谋的宙域
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.97,0:01:54.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在确认识别码
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.70,0:01:56.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但肯定是友军
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.15,0:01:59.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贝特中尉的小队正在急速赶去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.90,0:02:02.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也是要参加这次阅舰式的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.00,0:02:04.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在两天后
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.40,0:02:06.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自一年战争以来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.60,0:02:10.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,联邦的高官们也总算是伸够懒腰了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.22,0:02:11.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说错了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.76,0:02:15.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阅舰式是以前就预定好的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.50,0:02:19.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本舰原来也应作为新锐舰参加的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.30,0:02:24.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幕僚会议强制举行阅舰式
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.10,0:02:28.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许是想显示联邦的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.40,0:02:31.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我并不认为那些家伙会宁事息人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.47,0:02:32.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特别是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.76,0:02:36.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个阿纳贝尔·卡多…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.56,0:02:41.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是贝特
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.80,0:02:42.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目测目标
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.25,0:02:44.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是战舰伯明翰
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.30,0:02:46.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挺逍遥的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.80,0:02:49.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,观阅旗舰居然没带护卫舰
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.50,0:02:53.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,观阅官应该是格林·怀亚特大将吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.66,0:03:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才的MS是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.30,0:03:02.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是阿尔比昂派出的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.96,0:03:06.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那艘不懂得变通的船吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.20,0:03:18.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被察觉了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.17,0:03:28.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浦木
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.95,0:03:30.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你丢下迟钝的Cannon不管了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.95,0:03:32.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\fs34\3c&H00ef877e}Cannon：这里指GM Cannon，RX-77-2 Guncannon的量产机\N为降低成本采用了RGM-79的框架、装甲等
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.26,0:03:38.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浪费太多子弹了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.90,0:03:40.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说是这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.63,0:03:41.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,废话也太多
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.90,0:03:50.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浦木！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.56,0:03:51.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绕过来了？！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.45,0:04:05.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.85,0:04:11.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被干掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.80,0:04:13.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赢了…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.92,0:04:16.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于赢了大尉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.24,0:04:22.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干得好，宏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.85,0:04:26.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你打赢大尉了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.60,0:04:27.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉斯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.80,0:04:30.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实战的话你已被击落了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.35,0:04:31.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,训练嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.53,0:04:33.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是打得快活点吧，宏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.70,0:04:35.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.73,0:04:36.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死性不改
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.34,0:04:41.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浦木
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.30,0:04:42.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干得好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.60,0:04:44.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去请你喝啤酒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.70,0:04:46.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全靠Full Burnern的性能
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.17,0:04:48.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是靠我技术
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.87,0:04:49.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.86,0:04:51.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已能运用它了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.17,0:04:54.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.76,0:04:55.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,状况结束
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.75,0:04:56.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.77,0:04:57.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.00,0:05:04.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也已是个老头了啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.50,0:05:10.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知还能乘它多久啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.73,0:05:18.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大尉！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.67,0:05:20.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前方有黑色物体
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.90,0:05:22.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很大！很大！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.07,0:05:23.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.60,0:05:32.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别吓人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.36,0:05:35.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是联络过的太空殖民地的移送嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.66,0:05:39.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为没有殖民地大小的实感
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.27,0:05:45.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把战祸中受损SIDE1的殖民地
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.90,0:05:47.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,运送到SIDE3
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.66,0:05:50.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是殖民地再生计划的第二阶段
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.26,0:05:55.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是…太空殖民地
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.23,0:06:03.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.51,0:06:04.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.66,0:06:05.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.75,0:06:12.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干得好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.93,0:06:14.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于击落了巴宁格
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.40,0:06:19.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是研究的成果啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.14,0:06:22.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,状况预测很直接
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.86,0:06:24.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这架GUNDAM会成长的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.18,0:06:27.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随着某位先生的战技等级一起成长
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.97,0:06:31.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为是我的GUNDAM嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.13,0:06:34.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.28,0:06:37.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，是我们的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.56,0:06:38.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.60,0:06:43.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.32,0:06:45.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么时候从“在下”改口成“我”了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.44,0:06:47.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.40,0:06:51.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对联邦的军官请别摆出大姐的架子哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.53,0:06:52.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.82,0:06:56.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种话等你敢吃胡萝卜了再说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.13,0:06:59.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的GUNDAM就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.04,0:07:09.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来没什么问题啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.27,0:07:13.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这阵子太疲劳了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.37,0:07:15.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要的话配点维生素给你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.42,0:07:16.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.43,0:07:18.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话就没关系了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.90,0:07:20.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.36,0:07:22.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过这是怎么回事呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.00,0:07:26.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脚骨折时还到处逃避治疗的大尉却…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.37,0:07:30.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是脚在一直叫我快逃快逃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.57,0:07:34.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是爱耍嘴皮子，证明很健康
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.47,0:07:35.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诊断完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.07,0:07:36.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.87,0:07:42.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有何不适？大尉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.54,0:07:43.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.10,0:07:44.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.72,0:07:45.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.64,0:07:46.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰长您难道…？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.80,0:07:47.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.06,0:07:51.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我被限制酒量了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.22,0:07:52.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被医生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.61,0:08:01.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天喝到这个刻度为止
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.24,0:08:03.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，得让我多喝一个刻度
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.92,0:08:05.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大尉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.82,0:08:07.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶尔陪我喝一杯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.80,0:08:10.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好酒一个人喝也没滋味啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.50,0:08:21.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么大家都吃得下这种东西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.88,0:08:23.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.58,0:08:25.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是男子汉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.30,0:08:28.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.70,0:08:29.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宏
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.30,0:08:33.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在搞什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.73,0:08:36.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不、不…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.00,0:08:40.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为妮娜老是把我当小孩子看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.90,0:08:44.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是当然，就算在绝大部分的少爷中
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.30,0:08:47.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你仍是最优秀的纯粹培养啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.30,0:08:49.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\fs34\3c&H00ef877e}纯粹培养：把生物从其他种类生物中分离出来\N只培养一个种类或一个系统的科学技术，主要用于微生物的培养
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.70,0:08:50.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了，我不是来谈这个的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.42,0:08:51.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞧这个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.63,0:08:53.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是？！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.68,0:08:55.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是蒙夏中尉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.16,0:08:58.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恋恋不舍，还在做这种事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.80,0:09:02.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是摩拉在GM的驾驶舱里发现的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.64,0:09:05.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞧，这张很棒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.90,0:09:07.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是怎么拍到的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.84,0:09:15.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过妮娜小姐有时确实会散发出妩媚的芳香呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.60,0:09:19.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是表现出拍照的蒙夏中尉的下流而已吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.50,0:09:20.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真急死人了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.82,0:09:24.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看不懂吗？那成熟的气息
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.22,0:09:25.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宏
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.07,0:09:29.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有GUNDAM做你的爱神丘比特
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.80,0:09:31.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有自信吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.84,0:09:37.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我问的是你和她能不能顺利进展啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.55,0:09:38.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喜欢她吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.00,0:09:39.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.05,0:09:41.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.52,0:09:42.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我爱她啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.55,0:09:49.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你不想更了解女性吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.63,0:09:51.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从头到脚地了解
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.25,0:09:59.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些小伙子如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.31,0:10:03.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在扎实地成长着
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.77,0:10:06.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,测试机师领悟得很快
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.25,0:10:07.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特别是浦木少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.10,0:10:11.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为有妮娜的支持吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.05,0:10:14.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使除去这个因素进步也很大吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.55,0:10:15.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.73,0:10:17.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公私双方面好像都受到她照顾呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.05,0:10:19.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.35,0:10:22.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来人事制度也有重新检讨的余地了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.38,0:10:27.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,年轻人真好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.44,0:10:29.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总是以胜利为目标
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.25,0:10:31.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.07,0:10:33.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴宁格老弟
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.21,0:10:35.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在地球上有位夫人…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.43,0:10:39.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实如此
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.66,0:10:41.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.40,0:10:44.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等作战告一段落就申请休假吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.45,0:10:45.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.67,0:10:47.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说他们有了成长
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.18,0:10:51.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也不是能和年轻人逞强的年纪了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.52,0:10:52.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.40,0:10:54.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这只是心态上的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.62,0:10:57.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你既然这么说了也不勉强
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.12,0:11:00.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.44,0:11:01.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大尉？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.75,0:11:03.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.10,0:11:07.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我与妻子以前就处于分居状态了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.62,0:11:09.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这真是…失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.40,0:11:11.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不、没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.47,0:11:16.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只想以机师的身份与迪拉兹战斗到最后而没有懊悔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.85,0:11:19.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彼此彼此
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.47,0:11:22.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.31,0:11:25.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本舰即将与补给舰会合
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.82,0:11:28.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也暂时去睡一会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.42,0:11:30.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也去休息一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.43,0:11:31.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.35,0:11:32.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢招待
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.35,0:11:48.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真想念啊，卡留斯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.00,0:11:49.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.55,0:11:51.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.68,0:11:55.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,302巡哨中队如今仅剩下3架了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.37,0:11:57.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他人也快到了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.60,0:12:00.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的心就像现在的宇宙一样振奋着
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.85,0:12:01.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.75,0:12:03.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也发生了奇怪的事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.53,0:12:05.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.54,0:12:07.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是关于希玛中佐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.55,0:12:10.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们差点就误降在希玛舰队上了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.98,0:12:12.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希玛·格拉罕…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.52,0:12:16.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她负责的应该是其它方向吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.35,0:12:34.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就快到达Z地点了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.32,0:12:36.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,联邦的那些家伙会来吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.51,0:12:38.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然会
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.20,0:12:40.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来的不是狐就是狸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.75,0:12:48.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到会合地点了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.24,0:12:49.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该不是陷阱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.15,0:12:51.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,备茶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.45,0:12:54.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喝大吉岭
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.45,0:12:56.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\fs34\3c&H00ef877e}大吉岭：产于印度孟加拉省的大吉岭一带的极品红茶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.70,0:13:19.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,补给舰艾治
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.88,0:13:20.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布莱特中尉以下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.15,0:13:23.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请求着舰许可
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.25,0:13:24.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准许
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.45,0:13:25.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎来到阿尔比昂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.05,0:13:30.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这回还有邮件哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.20,0:13:33.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.40,0:13:39.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平民的阿纳海姆的巴普尔顿小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.45,0:13:41.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.55,0:13:44.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉斯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.95,0:13:46.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这个家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.20,0:13:48.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和蒙夏中尉那色鬼一样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.35,0:13:50.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不、不是啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.71,0:13:55.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照片全都在宏那家伙手里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.45,0:13:58.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种偷窥狂的照片，你卖了多少钱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.65,0:14:01.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不懂女人心的臭家伙！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.95,0:14:03.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎、怎么搞的？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.10,0:14:05.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相、相信我啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.75,0:14:08.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好，从实招来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.40,0:14:12.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.05,0:14:13.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不要呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.30,0:14:14.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宏，救我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.12,0:14:15.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉斯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.98,0:14:17.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们必须去值班啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.30,0:14:20.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浦木少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.55,0:14:22.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照片在哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.40,0:14:23.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不老实交代的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.78,0:14:25.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不饶你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.30,0:14:27.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那、那些都丢进碎纸机了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.55,0:14:28.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睁眼说瞎话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.90,0:14:30.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摩拉，住手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.54,0:14:33.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在还在看这种书的他
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.10,0:14:35.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的会做那种事吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.78,0:14:37.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那、那是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.40,0:14:39.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,《女性的知识ABC》
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.90,0:14:41.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,《宇宙住民女性论》
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.15,0:14:44.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,《女体的神秘》
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.35,0:14:49.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底在看什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.70,0:14:53.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浦木、吉斯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.00,0:14:55.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们在干什么？！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.13,0:14:58.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这种地方偷懒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.35,0:14:59.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,值班怎么办？！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.62,0:15:01.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大尉，这是因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.01,0:15:04.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别撒娇
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.45,0:15:06.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们的松懈会让船沉没的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.32,0:15:08.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浦木
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.23,0:15:09.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也一样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.50,0:15:10.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.34,0:15:11.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.81,0:15:14.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就行了吗？！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.95,0:15:18.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.75,0:15:29.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说着就来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.22,0:15:30.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以后再教训你们
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.80,0:15:31.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.43,0:15:32.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.35,0:15:33.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜，快点
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.25,0:15:43.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,报告情况
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.54,0:15:46.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,经米诺夫斯基干涉波的反探测测知疑似战舰的反应
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.15,0:15:48.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,5-1-9
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.35,0:15:51.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在伯明翰的附近啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.61,0:15:53.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MS的出动如何了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.26,0:15:55.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立刻就出动
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.73,0:15:56.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太慢了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.70,0:15:58.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫贝特他们也准备好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.13,0:16:20.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还以为女士总要别人等待呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.70,0:16:22.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是海军陆战队
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.66,0:16:24.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交涉看来也有点棘手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.47,0:16:25.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.35,0:16:27.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女士都喜欢礼物的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.52,0:16:29.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是定律
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.80,0:16:32.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.60,0:16:34.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔比昂的紧急来电
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.14,0:16:35.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,读吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.85,0:16:36.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.04,0:16:38.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们发现敌舰影
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.10,0:16:41.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已派MS急速赶去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.30,0:16:42.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发信 阿尔比昂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.71,0:16:45.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受信 观阅舰队司令
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.25,0:16:45.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.15,0:16:46.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.08,0:16:48.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发什么情啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.00,0:16:51.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确像高云麾下的舰只
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.34,0:16:52.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.17,0:16:56.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反转了！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.40,0:16:57.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯明翰反转！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.65,0:16:58.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.73,0:16:59.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出卖我们？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.69,0:17:01.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别慌张！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.25,0:17:03.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.85,0:17:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.04,0:17:06.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌舰开炮！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.78,0:17:14.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尼贝伦格沉没！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.55,0:17:19.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是要让我逃走啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.72,0:17:22.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是在做戏给友军看
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.55,0:17:24.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以没打中这艘船
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.05,0:17:26.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确是个好男人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.37,0:17:35.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是伯明翰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.18,0:17:37.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在逃离时还击沉了一艘
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.10,0:17:38.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2时方向
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.17,0:17:40.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2艘逃跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.05,0:17:46.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我绝不会忘的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.35,0:17:47.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那艘船是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.55,0:17:48.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷静点！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.68,0:17:52.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的目的是掩护伯明翰撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.65,0:17:56.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是那家伙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.06,0:17:59.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被修理了还不学乖吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.19,0:18:05.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别浪费弹药
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.49,0:18:26.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.65,0:18:27.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蚱蜢吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.72,0:18:29.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在贝特中尉他们到达之前…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.62,0:18:31.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要利用形势！浦木
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.40,0:18:32.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.90,0:18:43.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在、在哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.62,0:18:46.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种时候就该躲起来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.35,0:18:51.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浦木他们呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.25,0:19:01.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希玛大人，差不多了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.07,0:19:03.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人估计也有增援
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.97,0:19:05.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道，我还不想找死
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.49,0:19:11.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面对3架敌机仍一边倒吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.19,0:19:15.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不、有一架没在动啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.10,0:19:17.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.45,0:19:23.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蚱蜢就交给巴格曼了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.90,0:19:31.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样或许
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.23,0:19:33.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能了解敌人的战力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.94,0:19:36.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.66,0:19:39.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还想从我希玛的买卖里抽成吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.55,0:19:51.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.72,0:19:52.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希玛大人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.53,0:19:54.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉莉·玛莲到了回收的极限距离
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.45,0:19:57.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也罢…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.92,0:20:00.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正会有麻烦的人是卡多
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.62,0:20:01.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.21,0:20:02.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撤
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.00,0:20:14.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大尉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.72,0:20:15.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没受伤吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.46,0:20:17.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.85,0:20:19.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中了一下弹
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.52,0:20:20.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.47,0:20:21.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔比昂很近
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.25,0:20:26.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗配置解除
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.85,0:20:28.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把贝特他们的小队也叫回来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.90,0:20:29.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.99,0:20:31.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,击落敌MS两架
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.10,0:20:34.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都是巴宁格大尉的战绩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.75,0:20:36.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,司考特，能接通吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.20,0:20:36.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.37,0:20:40.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了不起啊，巴宁格大尉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.31,0:20:41.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.75,0:20:43.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实我还有另一个战果
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.07,0:20:45.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,归舰后立刻向你汇报
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.92,0:20:48.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我可要好好期待了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.80,0:20:49.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.45,0:20:52.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下，大尉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.20,0:20:54.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出击前的事我听说了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.55,0:20:56.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就暂且原谅他们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.14,0:20:58.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.56,0:21:11.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大尉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.55,0:21:14.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我似乎是太松懈了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.89,0:21:17.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然伯明翰没受损
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.60,0:21:19.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但如果出击得太迟…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.95,0:21:22.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我从摩拉那听说了事情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.35,0:21:25.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是蒙夏那家伙拍的照片吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.25,0:21:26.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.05,0:21:27.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.79,0:21:28.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,处理掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.10,0:21:29.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.95,0:21:31.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什、什么？！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.40,0:21:32.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一张也没留？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.12,0:21:34.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.31,0:21:35.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个多疑的家伙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.10,0:21:39.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才会被当做孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.41,0:21:42.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们已能独当一面了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.01,0:21:46.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才也和敌人势均力敌地战斗着
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.45,0:21:49.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,往后就看你们是否能切实体会
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.97,0:21:51.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是我无法教的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.45,0:21:53.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.29,0:21:57.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话以前也说过吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.73,0:21:59.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在夜色中的澳大利亚…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.00,0:22:03.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只记得做俯卧撑了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.32,0:22:05.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.95,0:22:12.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浦木
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.95,0:22:14.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉斯说的没错
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.21,0:22:16.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少也该留下一张的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.64,0:22:19.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大尉也带着那种东西吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.15,0:22:21.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.37,0:22:23.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也很不中用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.62,0:22:26.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过还不至于像你那样
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.71,0:22:29.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说教结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.71,0:22:39.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.80,0:22:41.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在着舰前…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.35,0:22:45.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基于海军令则
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.83,0:22:47.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星尘作战
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.35,0:22:49.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所罗门海域实施纲要
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.01,0:22:51.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.68,0:22:53.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌方的配置一目了然啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.75,0:22:56.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GUNDAM2号机？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.05,0:22:57.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大尉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.85,0:22:58.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.05,0:22:59.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是卡多吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.51,0:23:01.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.35,0:23:02.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浦木
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.25,0:23:03.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡多要行动了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.54,0:23:06.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们的目的是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.58,0:23:08.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们的目的…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.85,0:23:10.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这、这是？！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.91,0:23:17.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大尉！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.93,0:23:26.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大尉！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.68,0:23:27.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回答！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.44,0:23:28.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大尉！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.62,0:23:33.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大尉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.80,0:23:35.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别放弃啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.05,0:23:39.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大尉！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.25,0:24:19.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴宁格大尉！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.01,0:24:24.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴宁格大尉！！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.33,0:24:35.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大尉
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.28,0:24:37.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.55,0:24:40.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大尉
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.21,0:24:56.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.10,0:24:58.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.25,0:24:59.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.22,0:25:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.85,0:25:05.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是寄给巴宁格大尉的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.41,0:25:07.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西尔维亚·巴宁格…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.11,0:25:09.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是夫人啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.21,0:25:14.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出击前没能交给他
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.20,0:25:15.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你，妮娜小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.62,0:25:17.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由我来回信吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.90,0:25:25.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本日
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.77,0:25:28.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本舰在对战舰伯明翰进行救援时
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.80,0:25:32.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去了优秀的战斗指挥官绍斯·巴宁格大尉
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.45,0:25:35.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我祝福他一路顺风
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.75,0:25:39.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以作战行动中的舰长特权
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.40,0:25:43.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,授予阿尔法·A·贝特和宏·浦木战时军衔
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.02,0:25:46.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各自晋升一级

